@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant "POST /api/posts" as API
participant JwtAuthFilter
participant PostController
participant PostService
participant PostRepository
database DB
User -> Frontend: Fill offer form + submit
Frontend -> API: POST /api/posts
API -> JwtAuthFilter: Validate bearer JWT
JwtAuthFilter --> API: Principal ok
API -> PostController: createPost(request)
PostController -> PostService: createPost(userId, dto)
PostService -> PostRepository: save(post)
PostRepository -> DB: INSERT posts
DB --> PostRepository: persisted post
PostRepository --> PostService: Post
PostService --> PostController: PostResponse
PostController --> Frontend: 201 Created
Frontend --> User: UI feed refresh
@enduml
